iv class="relative"><img alt="Proveedor de atención médica y paciente colaborando en el monitoreo de salud" loading="lazy" width="600" height="450" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-auto max-h-[600px] object-cover" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fshared-health-monitoring.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fshared-health-monitoring.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fshared-health-monitoring.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Customer Success Stories</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->Virtual Practice platform is delivering next-generation medical care. As a multidisciplinary team, we find it powerful and intuitive for organizing patient cases, with clear medical records that support precise documentation and effective care.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Georgios Leon - Metabolic Specialist</p><p class="text-gray-600">Precision Medicine Startup, Greece</p></div></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->It&#x27;s been an easy, practical and reliable tool to manage my medical records. It has many useful tools that had saved me not only time but also lives because I can access patient files from my phone wherever I am.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Nery Orozco</p><p class="text-gray-600">Vascular Surgeon, Guatemala</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What are Health Trackers in the Virtual Practice?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Health Trackers are a library of 70+ parameters — from vitals and labs to lifestyle metrics — that patients and providers can record. All data is stored inside the patient's electronic health record (EHR)."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do Health Trackers improve care for providers?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"They provide a continuous view of patient health between visits, power Remote Patient Monitoring care plans, and make longitudinal trends visible during consultations."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can patients log their own health data?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patients can log readings manually through the portal or mobile app, as well as sync data from devices and health apps."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which devices and health apps are supported?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Health Trackers connect with Bluetooth-enabled monitors, wearables, and popular platforms like Apple Health (iOS) and Google Health Connect (Android)."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can providers add measurements during visits?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Absolutely. Providers can add vitals or other measurements taken during in-person or telehealth consultations, ensuring the EHR is always up to date."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do Health Trackers support Remote Patient Monitoring (RPM)?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Tracker data is the foundation of RPM care plans. Providers can set personalized thresholds, assign monitoring teams, and receive alerts when readings fall outside the safe range."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Are patients actively involved with Health Trackers?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patients can view their own data, track progress toward goals, and collaborate with providers through shared monitoring and feedback loops."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do Health Trackers integrate with AI features?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Tracker data in the EHR provides context for AI Scribe, helping providers generate richer, more accurate consultation notes."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can clinics customize which trackers are available?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Admins choose which subset of the 70+ trackers is relevant for their practice or individual patients."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is tracker data secure and compliant?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. All data is stored securely within the EHR and managed under strict healthcare privacy and security standards."}}]}</script><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8"><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="What are Health Trackers in the Virtual Practice?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">What are Health Trackers in the Virtual Practice?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="How do Health Trackers improve care for providers?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">How do Health Trackers improve care for providers?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="Can p